sub_title: Professional in Forest and Nature Conservation and IT student
summary:
Forest- and Nature Conservation professional, trained in the areas of production, use, management and recovery of renewable natural resources (soil, water and forests, associated facilities and their relationship with ecosystems), with a keen interest in research, IT and management.

I continue to keep up-to-date with developments in my areas of interest and  my field of qualification.

Ease and willingness to learn, good interpersonal relations, responsible, creative, analytical and organized. Ability to work with interdisciplinary teams.
